      <title>据说 Canva 持有者即将扩大 15 亿美元的股票发售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/canva-holders-are-said-to-near-expanded-1-5-billion-share-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，澳大利亚软件公司 Canva Inc. 即将完成股票发行，预计筹集资金超过 15 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-21/canva-holders-are-said-to-near-expanded-1-5-billion-share-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 01:54:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
